        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Appendix B: Form - Confidentiality Statement"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "All persons accessing classified information must complete and submit a Confidentiality Statement to their immediate supervisor or company point-of-contact."
        }
